# Bitwise Academy — Firebase Architecture Map

## Knowledge Graph Summary

I created **40 entities** and **88 relations** in graph memory, covering every layer of the app's Firebase integration.

---

## Firebase Services Used

| Service | Purpose | Emulator Port |
|---|---|---|
| **Firebase Auth** | Email/Password, Google, Apple sign-in | 9099 |
| **Cloud Firestore** | All app data (users, exams, attempts, quests, skins) | 8080 |
| **Firebase Storage** | Skin images, exam file attachments | 9199 |

