```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph Firestore
        U["users/{uid}"]
        AW["admin_whitelist/{email}"]
        E["exams/{examId}"]
        Q["exams/{examId}/questions/{qId}"]
        AT["attempts/{attemptId}"]
        QU["quests/{questId}"]
        S["skins/{skinId}"]
    end

    subgraph Storage
        SS["skins/{filename}"]
        EA["exam_assets/{examId}/{file}"]
    end

    E --> Q
    S -.->|imageUrl| SS
    E -.->|attachmentUrl| EA
```

| Collection | Key Fields | Accessed By |
|---|---|---|
| `users/{uid}` | uid, email, displayName, role, xp, level, coins, streakDays, avatarUrl, unlockedAvatars[], createdAt, lastLoginAt | AuthRepositoryImpl, UserRepository |
| `admin_whitelist/{email}` | *(existence check only)* | AuthRepositoryImpl |
| `exams/{examId}` | title, description, subject, difficultyTier, status, xpReward, questionCount | ExamRepository |
| `exams/{examId}/questions/{qId}` | questionText, questionType, options[], correctAnswer, explanation, points, order | ExamRepository |
| `attempts/{attemptId}` | userId, examId, score, totalPoints, xpEarned, status, answers{} | AttemptRepository |
| `quests/{questId}` | title, description, type, targetValue, xpReward, iconName, isActive | QuestRepository |
| `skins/{skinId}` | name, price, imageUrl, createdAt | StoreRepository |

