## Summary Stats

- **40 graph entities** created (app, 3 Firebase services, 6 repositories, 5 BLoCs, 6 data models, 12 UI screens, 7 Firestore collections, 2 Storage paths, + DI and Router)
- **88 relations** mapped (dependency chains, data flows, routing, read/write patterns)
- **3 Firebase services** integrated: Auth, Firestore, Storage
- **7 Firestore collections** + 1 sub-collection documented
- **4 architectural gaps** identified
